com.ihealth.communication.control

Class Bg1Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ihealth.communication.control.Bg1Profile

  • public class Bg1Profile
extends java.lang.Object
    Public APIs for the Bg1 serials device profiles

    Clients need to register BroadcastReceiver to receive these Actions.
